font <- 'Karla'


theme_set(theme_minimal(base_family = font))

theme_update(
  plot.margin = margin(25, 15, 15, 25),
  plot.background = element_rect(color = "#ffffff", fill = "#ffffff"),
  panel.grid.major.x = element_line(color = "grey95",size = 0.6),
  panel.grid.major.y = element_blank(),
  panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
  axis.text = element_text(family = font),
  axis.text.x = element_text(color = "grey40",size = 15,margin = margin(t = 10,b = 10)),
  

  axis.text.y = element_blank(),
  axis.title = element_blank(),
  axis.ticks = element_blank(),
  plot.title = element_text(family = font, face = "bold", size = 17.45),
  plot.subtitle = element_textbox_simple(family = font, color = "grey40", size = 10.8,
                                         lineheight = 1.3, margin = margin(t = 5, b = 30)),
  plot.caption = element_text(family = font, color = "grey55", 
                              size = 10.5, margin = margin(t = 20, b = 0, r = 15))
)
